GOIN' ON A SECRET MISSION / FLYING KITES OR
MAYBE FISHIN' / I WANT THIS TER-/ -IFFIC

MISTER / HERE / BY MY SIDE * Well, I'd better.
I'm going to be a pop star just like her!

Wowsy-powsy! Liza... You sing just like
flash-in-the-pan pop sensation Kitty Purry!

Can I be a pop star like
you and Kitty Purry

someday pretty please?!
GOIN' ON A SECRET MISSION

/ FLYING KITES (OFF) OR MAYBE FISHIN' / I WANT
THIS TER-/ -IFFIC MISTER / HERE / BY MY SIDE...

Why don't you pick your own talent, Kid?
The family doesn't need

two singers. What you really need
to do is find your own thing.
And how can I figure out what my thing is?

It's not very hard. Just figure out
what your talent is and go do it.

Go do it! Wait... How... can I
tell what my talent is?

You have to find it for yourself.
Just try lots of stuff...
Liza! I think I should be a doctor!

Sounds pretty good. Just as long as you pick
something other than singing we'll be fine here
Doctor, I don't have time for a check-up now.

Yeah, you do... TELL ME HOW HAVE YOU BEEN FEELING
/ IF YOU'RE SICK, I'LL BE THERE HEALING-
There aren't any singing doctors!

Interesting blood pressure... You
seem a little stressed out.
Now we'll just check your reflexes!

O 'Kay, that's enough... Go
and hammer your own knee.
You're a very sick puppy. But I can fix that.
Just one little shot, alright?
You are not giving me a shot!
Yes I am! Get ready...
You stay away from me!!

So! Kid, maybe becoming a
doctor isn't your thing.
RIDIN' BIKES OR GETTIN' MUDDY...

Liza!... I'm going to be a hairdressler! Can I
get a little practice time in with your hair?
Are you nuts? You are not touching my hair!

Why?... I came up with a new song
for the occasion... YOU'LL LOOK

GOOD / THE WAY YOU SHOULD / THEY
GAVE SCISSORS TO A TODDLER...

Oh, fine! But no more singing! And you better
not... actually cut a single hair on my head.
Masterpiece... Just cast your eyes on the beauty!
Is there a problem?
Everybody's a critic.
Liza!! Now I'm going to be an animal trainer!!
Oh, please! Do not make me be your animal!
Well, I have to practice... Don't I?

THIS SWITCH IS REALLY REALLY STING...
Y / SO YOU BETTER JUST JUMP RIGHT

THROUGH THIS RINGY!... That's it!! I
am all done being your guinea pig!
Jump through the ring! Or I will sing!!
Never!

Well, darn... She won't obey me. Animal
training must not be my thing either...

Kid!!! Stop!! That's enough! Forget the drums...
I think we'll all be happier if you just sing.
Are you saying that my talent is for singing?

I'm saying... that singing is safer... than
all the other things you've been trying...

GOIN' ON A SECRET MISSION /
FLYING KITES OR MAYBE FISHIN'

/ I WANT THIS TER-/ -IFFIC
SISTER / HERE / BY MY SIDE /

RIDIN' BIKES OR GETTING' MUDDY
/ HOW I LOVE MY BESTEST BUDDY

/ THERE'S NO OTHER / LIKE THE
BROTHER / DEAR / BY MY SIDE...
